EmailTemplate.description: Sent to SPD Partner to get their insurance requirement
EmailTemplate.name: OB: Insurance Requirement
EmailTemplate.subject: SunPower | {!Account.Name}: Insurance Requirements
EmailTemplate.textOnly:
Dear {!Contact.FirstName}:
Thank you for partnering with SunPower and signing the SunPower Direct (SPD) and New Homes Master Subcontract Agreement.
As next step, please submit evidence of your insurance as below (required within 30 days of MSA Execution).
Insurance requirements are detailed in the MSA in Exhibit F. Please review and provide evidence of your coverage to include:
· Commercial General Liability
· Excess/Umbrella Coverage
· Commercial Auto Liability Coverage
· Workers’ Compensation/Employer’s Liability
· Builder’s Risk or Installation Floater & Inland Marine
Please provide the Certificate of Insurance in the form of attached sample Acord Form.
Please send the Certificate of Insurance to RLCProjectAdmin@sunpowercorp.com by (Date) so that we can ensure business continuity.
Please contact your Installation Partner Manager (IPM) for any questions or clarifications.
We look forward to growing our business with you.
Sincerely,
RLC Project Admin
